<title><![CDATA[开源免费播放器 VLC Media Player(VideoLAN)]]></title> 
<author>renjihe1988 &lt;admin@yourname.com&gt;</author>
<category><![CDATA[工具]]></category>
<pubDate>Mon, 24 Sep 2012 06:13:12 +0000</pubDate> 
<guid>http://i.renjihe.com/blog/read.php?3232</guid> 
